data.description: OPEN HOUSE SAT, MAR 25TH 1-2PM! Fabulous K. Hovnanian home in Inspiration. Just gorgeous in & out, shows like a model! Cute FRONT PORCH greets you on drive up. Interior features beautiful HARDWOOD FLOORING, modern neutral colors, recessed lighting. Floor to ceiling stone fireplace in family room open to kitchen with huge island, GRANITE COUNTERS, SS appliances, & GAS COOKTOP. Formal dining could be STUDY. Elegant master suite with garden tub. Upstairs GAME ROOM. Covered patio overlooks backyard. Don't miss out!
